Negotiations
In order to meet with Gray Leaf - the leader of the Green clan - you must make a sign using the Sacred Flower, which the forest people use when they need to hold talks with other clans.
#subobj 1
Reach the meeting area
The forest people of all clans use a well-defined place to hold talks.
#subobj 2
Summon the forest people
To broadcast a signal, place a Sacred Flower on an old trunk.
